attributeList.attribute: Cargo adaptor complex that mediates the sorting of specific plasma membrane proteins into vesicles at the trans-Golgi network. Forms a coat structure on vesicles involved in exocytosis of specific cargo proteins, including chitin synthase CHS3 (P29465), from the trans-Golgi network to the cell surface. Recruited by GTP-bound ARF1 (P11076).
